{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 328.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She had enough problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In October of '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the transports were going, and they were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have been called up as a family, no questions asked, and we went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were, I think, three in front of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we were the fourth one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would have to look into, into-- I think we were the fourth one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, they were so very, very stupid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was called an invalid, OK?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Theresienstadt, he was advised-- would-- I mean, to this day, I cannot believe it, and it's true.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was advised-- before the transport, we were called up, and I don't know who was the advisor, but it must have been somebody from the-- from the-- who, who was doing the transports.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was told the first thing he should do where he arrives, wherever it is-- because they did not know-- as far as I know, he didn't-- to go to the commandant and tell him that he is disabled.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now can you imagine that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, they would have-- as soon as they stripped him of his clothes, they would have found out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is no point in saying that he could have been saved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the point that in Theresienstadt somebody who was in the upper echelon, as far as I understood, of knowledge where these transport were supposed to go, to give a man an advice like that is a beyond my imagination.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How were you notified about the transport?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, jeez.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they just came to your accommodation and they called you up.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
